divs: Sighting DetailsWent ouside and saw an object in the sky, at first thougt it was a plane but there was no noise. It moved from the south and was traveling north. It was moving at about the speed of a small plane. When it got more into the northern sky, it stopped, for about a minute, then it continued moving northerly and disappeared.I thought it looked like a boomerang with red lights on the outer edges.
